      <title>汽车制造商在美国高级市场上迈出了税款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/car-makers-trail-us-high-grade-market-with-tariffs-set-to-hit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统对汽车进口的25％关税并警告未来一场更广泛的贸易战后，汽车制造商的债券在美国债务市场中削弱了。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-27/car-makers-trail-us-high-grade-market-with-tariffs-set-to-hit</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 27 Mar 2025 16:28:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当美国库存下降覆盖更广泛的贸易战时，石油边缘上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-27</link>
      <description><![CDATA[石油越来越高，因为更紧密的近期供应平衡的迹象掩盖了一场加剧的全球贸易战，威胁到全球能源消耗。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-march-27</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 23:30:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着贸易战的云层经济前景：市场包裹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美国对汽车制造商的关税提前提前，股票激起了人们对扩大贸易战和抵消数据的担忧，这些数据显示出全球最大经济体的增长速度快。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-03-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 26 Mar 2025 22:44:23 GMT</pubDate>
